away with the Cirque

00:10:13.090 --> 00:10:14.340
and joining the Cirque family.

00:10:14.340 --> 00:10:16.548
HEATHER RILEY: Well, I've
been with the Cirque family

00:10:16.548 --> 00:10:18.670
now about 15 years,
just over 15 years.

00:10:18.670 --> 00:10:22.240
And my original career, I was
an elementary school teacher.

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.909
So not much of a difference
between classroom and working

00:10:24.909 --> 00:10:25.450
with artists.

00:10:25.450 --> 00:10:27.430
But-- no.

00:10:27.430 --> 00:10:28.510
With all due respect.

00:10:28.510 --> 00:10:29.170
No.

00:10:29.170 --> 00:10:30.586
It was actually a
company I worked

00:10:30.586 --> 00:10:33.640
