called Up with People, which

00:10:33.640 --> 00:10:36.520
was a different format,
but also in the performing

00:10:36.520 --> 00:10:37.470
arts and leadership.

00:10:37.470 --> 00:10:38.845
And it was a
colleague from there

00:10:38.845 --> 00:10:41.064
